desc_long							评测						“The puzzles themselves, and clearly this is the most important point, are sublime. They are so well designed, so utterly brilliant in construction and delivery, that I wonder at Brown’s brain. There’s even a wit to them, moments that make me smile as I play, as I realise how carefully and deliberately a puzzle has been designed...”Rock Paper Shotgun												关于这款游戏							Hexcells Plus is a standalone expansion to Hexcells that contains 36 new and more challenging puzzles.						
